I'm thrilled to see this innovative approach to fostering inclusive communication among neurodiverse children. The integration of such a tangible, user-centered solution is truly groundbreaking. By empowering the children themselves in the design process, you've not only enhanced the effectiveness of the technology but also cultivated a deeper sense of agency and pride in their own experiences.

The use of color as a universal language for play and interaction is both brilliant and practical. It aligns beautifully with your aim of supporting empathy and mutual understanding.